    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Empire employment agency\ntoday took change of venue from\nJustice Suckers court in the\nthree cases recently begun against\n1t for the alleged defrauding of\nforeigners who were sold jobs on\nthe 0. r. & N. at Conan, Wash,\nthat did not after materialize, it is\nalleged. Justice Stocker sent the\ncases to Justice Hyde's court.\n\n\nThe prosecutions were instituted\nby Attorneys Tustin e. Moore, who\nhave been retained by the Indus\ntrial Workers Of the World to\nprosecute employment agency\ncases."
